上通天文，下晓地理的人里面最能吹牛的那个就是。</div></div></div></div></div><div class="ArticleItem-extraInfo"><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">149 人<!-- -->也赞了该文章</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="headline" content="200万年前一个基因缺陷，让人类祖先凭双腿跑到了食物链顶端"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https:////zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/45881719"/><meta itemProp="datePublished" content="2018-10-02T15:11:05.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-10-02T15:11:05.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="19"/><meta itemProp="image"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="articleBody">每年国庆都有人问有什么景点推荐，我一般会回答，瘫床上。国庆出门的人，大多有不长记性的特点。上高速，走不动；坐高铁，抢不到票；去景区，全是人；去爬山，没体力。总的来说，太累，出去一趟还不够受罪，哪还有力气出去。 最关键的是，<b>现在年轻人天天加班，日常996，再加上熬夜、垃圾食品的摧残，想出去玩一趟，却发现体力越来越跟不上了。</b>爬5楼都要喘半天，爬个500米的小山坡还不得丢半条命？要是百万年前的祖先知道现代人是…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->149</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button 